---
title: Chermoula Chicken Couscous Bowl with Mint Salad & Yoghurt
description: Savour the flavours of chermoula spices on juicy, tender chicken with fluffy couscous and a fresh and fragrant mint salad. A dollop of creamy yoghurt brings it all together, balancing bold spice with a cool, tangy finish. Perfect for a flavourful weeknight escape!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
